125
00:09:55.553 --> 00:09:56.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
私が何か？

126
00:09:56.971 --> 00:09:58.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
文化部の究極のメニューは

127
00:09:58.681 --> 00:10:02.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
食文化の本質を
見極めようというのが目的だ

128
00:10:02.143 --> 00:10:04.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
それをチャラチャラ
ファッション化されたら

129
00:10:04.645 --> 00:10:05.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
たまらないんだよ

130
00:10:06.105 --> 00:10:08.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
