143
00:10:52.652 --> 00:10:54.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
分かりました

144
00:10:55.154 --> 00:10:58.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
