229
00:17:34.678 --> 00:17:37.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
局長はイノシシ鍋を
食べた事があるんですか？

230
00:17:38.891 --> 00:17:43.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
